# Strong sightglass suite — 39 in-tree kernels with goldens regenerated by
# wasmtime 43.0.1 (independent oracle). Same kernel names as upstream
# sightglass, but binaries are recompiled with strengthened workloads (see
# notes/benchmarking/sightglass_strong.md) so tier-1-only workTimeUs lands
# in [5s, 10s], giving tier-2 a measurable post-swap window. `noop` is the
# only kernel kept at upstream size, as a harness-overhead reference point.
#
# Layout: <kernel>/benchmark.wasm (per-kernel-dir, sightglass-cli native).
# Paths use ${REPO_ROOT} which the sweep driver exports.

${REPO_ROOT}/test/ir/testdata/sightglass-strong/blake3-scalar/benchmark.wasm
